OL,3,CThames Water's finance chief quits as
OL,4,Cfirm continues trying to find a buyer
OL,6,FThames Water's finance boss has quit
OL,7,Fmidway through a key restructuring of
OL,8,Fthe heavily indebted utility giant.
OL,10,FChief financial officer Alastair
OL,11,FCochran told the firm that he is
OL,12,Fstepping down on Friday morning, the
OL,13,FPA news agency understands.
OL,15,FHis sudden departure comes as Thames
OL,16,FWater continues to try to find a buyer
OL,17,Ffor the company to help steady its
OL,18,Ffinances.
