OL,3,CThames Water's finance chief quits as
OL,4,Cfirm continues trying to find a buyer
OL,6,FThames Water is England's biggest
OL,7,Fwater firm, with about 16 million
OL,8,Fcustomers.
OL,10,FIt is in at least #16 billion of debt,
OL,11,Fand recently won court approval to
OL,12,Ftake out as much as #3 billion more in
OL,13,Floans, in a deal designed to keep it
OL,14,Frunning into 2026.
OL,16,FMr Cochran, who was at Thames Water
OL,17,Ffor three-and-a-half years, was
OL,18,F"instrumental" in securing a #3
OL,19,Fbillion deal, according to chief
OL,20,Fexecutive Chris Weston.
