OL,3,CThames Water's finance chief quits as
OL,4,Cfirm continues trying to find a buyer
OL,6,FA source with knowledge of the
OL,7,Fsituation said Mr Cochran notified the
OL,8,Fcompany of his departure early on
OL,9,FFriday. He will remain in post until
OL,10,Fthe end of March.
OL,12,FIt constitutes another setback for the
OL,13,Fcompany, which has been at the centre
OL,14,Fof growing public anger over the state
OL,15,Fof the privatised water industry, as
OL,16,Fconsumers face steeply rising bills
OL,17,Fwhile companies pump raw sewage into
OL,18,Frivers and waterways.
