OL,3,CThames Water's finance chief quits as
OL,4,Cfirm continues trying to find a buyer
OL,6,FThat is despite a succession of
OL,7,Fpenalties from regulators Ofwat and
OL,8,Fthe Environment Agency.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, many bosses, including
OL,11,Fthose at Thames Water, have still been
OL,12,Fgiven hefty bonuses in the last year.
OL,14,FChairman Sir Adrian Montague added
OL,15,Fthat Mr Cochran had "overseen
OL,16,Fsignificant changes" to the company
OL,17,Fwhile in the position.
