OL,3,CThames Water's finance chief quits as
OL,4,Cfirm continues trying to find a buyer
OL,6,F"He has led the work to put (Thames
OL,7,FWater's) finances on a more stable
OL,8,Ffooting, overseeing the first stages
OL,9,Fof our equity raise and financial
OL,10,Frestructuring, laying the foundations
OL,11,Ffor the wholesale recapitalisation of
OL,12,Fthe business."
OL,14,FStuart Thom, Thames' current director
OL,15,Fof group finance, will be interim
OL,16,Fchief financial officer.
